message: "More than 10 men from El Paso were arrested in a human trafficking operation last week, officials say."

data.description: More than 10 men from El Paso were arrested in a human trafficking operation last week.The four day operation began Monday.The investigation uncovered that 13 men knowingly agreed to pay a fee to engage in sexual conduct, according to the Texas Department
data.title: El Pasoans accused of trying to pay for sex
